nt|If you have tried ^*BBridge Base Online^*N you will have seen various bridge information and quizzes displayed in the lobby area of that program. One of those quizzes is based on a similar card combination (@SQ10987 opposite @SA2). It is stated there that the correct play for 4 tricks is to make the strange play of leading the @SQ from the dummy on the first round of the suit!|
