nt|This deal took place toward the end of one of the most remarkable days of bridge in Fred's career. Fred and Brad started the second day of the 2001 Cavendish in a rather dismal 41st (out of 52 pairs). They posted the biggest scores in both of the 2 sessions on the second day to climb all the way to first place! |
