nt|Unfortunately, they dropped to 8th on the final day, but it was a real thrill for Fred and Brad to move up so far in the standings so quickly. They won a lot of IMPs on this deal because only about half of the North-South pairs bid slam and Fred was the only declarer in 6NT to find the winning play (the other declarers cashed the @SA first and then led the @S10 to dummy's @SQ).|
