hs|nsss|nt|The North-South spade combination is pretty obscure and, even in an event of the quality of the Cavendish, most of the experts were not familiar with the correct way to play this suit. Fortunately for Fred, he had spent considerable time studying card combinations and this one has always been one of his favorites. |
